Set Height 750
Source "recordings/tapes/shared-config.tape"
Output "recordings/svgs/tools/list-toolkit-gmail-limit-3.svg"
Output "recordings/ascii/tools/list-toolkit-gmail-limit-3.ascii"

Hide
Type "# List with --limit flag"
Enter
Show
Type "composio tools list --toolkits gmail --limit 3"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 6s
